  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.\r\n</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nREASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.\r\n</p>",
    "<p>The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this permission.</p><p><br></p><p>\r\n</p><p>\r\nREASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).</p><p>\r\n</p>",
    "&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; margin: 0cm;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;Prior to the first occupation of the development hereby approved two swift brick or swift boxes shall be installed in accordance with the manufacturer’s specification, which shall be retained in perpetuity thereafter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; margin: 0cm;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; margin: 0cm;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;REASON: In the interests of promoting biodiversity in the area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed extensions to Nos. 47 and 49 Mildenhall Road, hereby permitted, shall commence and be completed together as one development.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;REASON: In order to safeguard the the local character and the amenities of neighbouring occupiers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-88340e6e-7fff-8875-04d5-4107d6999d78&quot;&gt;The approved first and second floor side elevation windows to 47 Mildenhall Road shall be opaque glazed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-88340e6e-7fff-8875-04d5-4107d6999d78&quot;&gt;REASON: To safeguard against loss of privacy and overlooking.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
